.TH HCXPIOFF "1"

.SH NAME
hcxpioff - control Raspberry Pi via GPIO

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B  hcxpioff <options>

.SH DESCRIPTION
.BI hcxdumptool
is a tool to control Raspberry Pi via GPIO (hardware modification required).

